<div id="review_522461708" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/522461708" />
    <a title="Sassy " class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7853405-sassy"><img alt="Sassy " src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1456073034p2/7853405.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/522461708?book_show_action=true">Jan 31, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sassy " class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sassy " href="/user/show/7853405-sassy">Sassy </a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer522461708" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7917233742942854393"><br/>&quot;KILTED DESIRE 1 - Sands of Betrayal&quot; by A.B McKinley, was full of action, suspense, steam and a very sexy Scot in a kilt. I started this book and could not put it down until I finished it in the wee hours of the morning. Our Hero, Scott and our feisty Heroine, Katie just kept me glued to the pages to see what was going to happen next with the trials of their relationship and how the dangerous mission that he was on was affecting both of their lives.<br/><br/>I did not care for Katie at first as I found h</span>
  <span id="freeText7917233742942854393" style="display:none"><br />"KILTED DESIRE 1 - Sands of Betrayal" by A.B McKinley, was full of action, suspense, steam and a very sexy Scot in a kilt. I started this book and could not put it down until I finished it in the wee hours of the morning. Our Hero, Scott and our feisty Heroine, Katie just kept me glued to the pages to see what was going to happen next with the trials of their relationship and how the dangerous mission that he was on was affecting both of their lives.<br /><br />I did not care for Katie at first as I found her too self involved and thought she was only out for herself. My opinion of her did change as the story unfolded.<br /><br />Scott is the image of every woman's dream... loving, caring, honest &amp; devoted to only one woman.<br /><br />The story was exciting with lots of action along with a very sensual love story that unfolds between Scott &amp; Katie that takes your breath away.<br /><br />I highly recommend this book to everyone and I am now going to download the next book to see what kind of trouble Scott gets into in this book. Will the love between Scott &amp; Katie be strong enough to survive?? We shall see what happens in the next book... "KILTED DESIRE 2 - Russian Roulette"<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="7917233742942854393" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
