<div id="review_210274927" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/210274927" />
    <a title="Sue" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3477736-sue"><img alt="Sue" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1320948914p2/3477736.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/210274927?book_show_action=true">Sep 18, 2011</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sue" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sue" href="/user/show/3477736-sue">Sue</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Debra Ytaes</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=scottish">scottish</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=sexy">sexy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=scotsman">scotsman</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=passionate">passionate</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=military">military</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=new-author">new-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=scots-american">scots-american</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=kilted-warrior">kilted-warrior</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3477736-sue?shelf=contemporary-romance">contemporary-romance</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer210274927&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer210274927" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer597145221491435761">I really liked this book. If you like stories about former military men returning to Iraq to work as a body guard you will like this book. Scott is divorced and Katie is in the process divorce when the meet &amp; the attraction is immediate &amp; intense. In order for them to be able to build a life together, Scott decides to return to Iraq to work as a personal body guard for six months. He is shocked and a little dismayed to find that his client is a beautiful and sexy woman executive named Britney. S</span>
  <span id="freeText597145221491435761" style="display:none">I really liked this book. If you like stories about former military men returning to Iraq to work as a body guard you will like this book. Scott is divorced and Katie is in the process divorce when the meet &amp; the attraction is immediate &amp; intense. In order for them to be able to build a life together, Scott decides to return to Iraq to work as a personal body guard for six months. He is shocked and a little dismayed to find that his client is a beautiful and sexy woman executive named Britney. She is very attracted to Scott and tried to seduce him but he is faithful to Katie. Scott proposes to Katie in one of the most romantic settings. Scott is injured by a car bomb and is in a coma with head injuries for a few weeks. A.B. Mckinley is a new author and I highly recommend this book.</span>
  <a data-text-id="597145221491435761" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


