        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3565304587" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4625917449643981671">I had come across this on scribd, and thought the blurb sounded like something I’d be in to (deranged wannabe OW) but it was choppy, jumped around a lot, and I ended up skimming most of it. It ends in a bit of a cliffy, and I can’t see that it was ever published, so I wouldn’t recommend getting into it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


