<div id="review_557151708" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/557151708" />
    <a title="Libby" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13973642-libby"><img alt="Libby" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1355202527p2/13973642.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/557151708?book_show_action=true">Mar 10, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Libby" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Libby" href="/user/show/13973642-libby">Libby</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer557151708" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6642738314840879755">WOW!!!<br/>In the past I have always stayed away from male authors with anything containing romance. But do you know what? This guy gets it - he really does! The emotion I felt was real. There were times when I couldn&apos;t read for the tears clouding my vision (frustrating but satisfying at the same time). Action, romance, frustration, sadness, it is all here and so very well delivered! Not one aspect is over or under done - the balance is perfect!<br/>I am not going to retell the story here, other reviewers</span>
  <span id="freeText6642738314840879755" style="display:none">WOW!!!<br />In the past I have always stayed away from male authors with anything containing romance. But do you know what? This guy gets it - he really does! The emotion I felt was real. There were times when I couldn't read for the tears clouding my vision (frustrating but satisfying at the same time). Action, romance, frustration, sadness, it is all here and so very well delivered! Not one aspect is over or under done - the balance is perfect!<br />I am not going to retell the story here, other reviewers have done it and the synopsis tells you what you need to know. You are just going to have to get it yourself to find out the rest. But the one thing I might touch on is the fact that some of it is based on his real life experiences - I have huge respect for the men and women of the armed forces who face these situations everyday. Thank you to you all!<br />It is very well written - the spelling and grammar are perfect...and the body on the cover is his! (nudge, nudge, wink, wink)<br />Now I'm off to read the sequel.<br />Well done Sir! ;) Well done!<br />Come and join myself and his other fans - you can find us at Scott McKinley Author/Cover Model on facebook <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="6642738314840879755" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


