  <span id="freeText14559479804066515175" style="display:none">Looking for a new book boyfriend? Look no further, meet Scott all round action man and such a romantic....<br /><br />Scott is is out the armed forces and has had a lot to deal with until he meets Katie, she turns his world around. He loves her so much his prepared to take a dangerous job in a foreign country. Even long distance you can feel there love for one another.<br /><br />Six months in a war torn country, protecting a woman that is used to getting what she wants....it's not going to be easy.<br /><br />You go through so many different emotions on this journey, it bought a few tears to my eyes too!<br /><br />The characters are very real, and even though Scott is an action man his soft and loveable and ooh so romantic! I haven't mentioned his Scottish accent, when Scott speaks it written as spoken and you hear a Scottish accent, sexy :) <br /><br />You will really enjoy this book, action, scheming, and romance.<br /><br />4.5 vampy and racey stars.<br /><br /><br />**I received an arc of this book a while ago now, but have finally read it to give an honest review**<br /><br /><br /><br /></span>
